title: Merge pull request #1 from NITenyaw/master
message:
Merge pull request #1 from NITenyaw/master

Few code quality improvements.

title: Removed public fields in the classes Phase, SubTask & Task and put getter- and…
message: Removed public fields in the classes Phase, SubTask & Task and put getter- and setter-methods in their place. 'In public classes, use accessor methods, not public fields' [Effective Java, Item 14] Also renamed the field 'category' to 'categories'.

title: Improved the code of the DetailActivity a little bit. Added a new class…
message: Improved the code of the DetailActivity a little bit. Added a new class 'PointOfInterest' which represents points of interests, that are read from the CSV-file. Mainly introduced this class to get rid of all those lists which all had to be accessed to get information about a single point...
